            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="text"> The VAT field only applies to EU companies that are VAT registered and have an EU VAT number. Once a valid number has been entered, the applied tax may be removed according to regulations about intra-community transactions. The VAT field should be left blank for anyone outside the European Union (companies and consumers) and also should be left blank for EU consumers and individuals (that are not VAT registered companies). </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqThree">
