          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFAQ">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="text"> Yes, you can add a new card for Mastercard and Visa, but you cannot change your card to PayPal or vice versa or change a PayPal email to another email. To change your card, go to your profile page, then under Billing you will see an 'Edit' button next to your card info. </p>
            </div>
